00:11:01.260 --> 00:11:03.650
They look different,
but anyway...

00:11:03.650 --> 00:11:15.540
How many people here have read
the newspaper today or online,

00:11:15.540 --> 00:11:19.430
something related
to the newspaper?

00:11:19.430 --> 00:11:29.870
How many people have read a
magazine in the last week?

00:11:29.870 --> 00:11:40.610
Anybody? How many people read
one book in the last year?

00:11:40.610 --> 00:11:41.910
[ Laughter ]

00:11:41.910 --> 00:11:45.730
How many people read
ten books in last year?

00:11:45.730 --> 00:11:48.050
Twenty books?

00:11:48.050 --> 00:11:49.800
Thirty books?

00:11:49.800 --> 00:11:51.230
Forty? Be honest.

