very hard to feel hopeful.

00:35:59.140 --> 00:36:02.510
And as a result, not only
is it hard to feel hopeful,

00:36:02.510 --> 00:36:06.730
but it's hard to create art
when you're not feeling hopeful.

00:36:06.730 --> 00:36:10.850
And one at of the ways I
find hope is by talking

00:36:10.850 --> 00:36:14.370
to the young people and talking
to the people who are engaging

00:36:14.370 --> 00:36:17.470
in the literature, and
very often traveling

00:36:17.470 --> 00:36:20.390
